query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(k mk mi_idx) NoHashJoin(it2 k mi_idx mk mi) NoMergeJoin(it1 it2 k mi mi_idx mk t kt) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS western_dark_production
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IN ('murder-in-title',
'pocket-knife')
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info > '10'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('English',
'Norwegian',
'Denish',
'Germany',
'German',
'Denmark',
'Swedish',
'USA',
'Danish',
'USA')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = mi.movie_id AND ( t.title like '%murder%' OR t.title like '%Murder%' OR t.title like '%Mord%') AND t.production_year > 1969
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind = 'episode';
